      <h3>Pre Construction</h3>
      <p>West Fork Construction works closely with the owners, architects, and trade contractors during the pre-construction phase to assist and improve on the design and construction of the project. Our company strongly believes that the hard work and thorough analysis provided during this stage of the project will reduce cost and expedite schedules during the construction phase. We collaborate with our customers, architects, and subcontractors to proactively eliminate construction problems.</p>
